  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_171",
    "english": "A giant worm-like demon beast that lives underground in the Demon Realm. It sometimes comes over to the human world, disturbing the ecosystem. It has a habit of spitting acidic poison to weaken its prey when hunting. The said poison is sometimes used as a natural cutting fluid in the Demon Realm.",
